    "attributes": {
        "action": "Mandatory drug tests & psychiatric psychological assessments for public servants",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "We call on all public servants to be subject to mandatory drug testing every 3 months, and mandatory psychological and psychiatric assessments annually. We also call on there to be a mandatory public disclosure of membership of groups, societies and organizations where oaths have been taken.",
